360HTMLConverter::HTMLConverter(const SimpleRange& range)
361 : m_start(makeContainerOffsetPosition(range.start))
362 , m_end(makeContainerOffsetPosition(range.end))
363{
364 _attrStr = adoptNS([[NSMutableAttributedString alloc] init]);
365 _documentAttrs = adoptNS([[NSMutableDictionary alloc] init]);
366 _baseURL = nil;
367 _textLists = adoptNS([[NSMutableArray alloc] init]);
368 _textBlocks = adoptNS([[NSMutableArray alloc] init]);
369 _textTables = adoptNS([[NSMutableArray alloc] init]);
370 _textTableSpacings = adoptNS([[NSMutableArray alloc] init]);
371 _textTablePaddings = adoptNS([[NSMutableArray alloc] init]);
372 _textTableRows = adoptNS([[NSMutableArray alloc] init]);
373 _textTableRowArrays = adoptNS([[NSMutableArray alloc] init]);
374 _textTableRowBackgroundColors = adoptNS([[NSMutableArray alloc] init]);
375 _fontCache = adoptNS([[NSMutableDictionary alloc] init]);
376 _writingDirectionArray = adoptNS([[NSMutableArray alloc] init]);
377
378 _defaultTabInterval = 36;
379 _domRangeStartIndex = 0;
380 _quoteLevel = 0;
381
382 _flags.isSoft = false;
383 _flags.reachedStart = false;
384 _flags.reachedEnd = false;
385
386 _caches = makeUnique<HTMLConverterCaches>();
387}

389HTMLConverter::~HTMLConverter() = default;
390
391AttributedString HTMLConverter::convert()
392{
393 if (m_start > m_end)
394 return { };
395
396 Node* commonAncestorContainer = _caches->cacheAncestorsOfStartToBeConverted(m_start, m_end);
397 ASSERT(commonAncestorContainer);
398
399 m_dataSource = commonAncestorContainer->document().frame()->loader().documentLoader();
400
401 Document& document = commonAncestorContainer->document();
402 if (auto* body = document.bodyOrFrameset()) {
403 if (PlatformColor *backgroundColor = _colorForElement(*body, CSSPropertyBackgroundColor))
404 [_documentAttrs setObject:backgroundColor forKey:NSBackgroundColorDocumentAttribute];
405 }
406
407 _domRangeStartIndex = 0;
408 _traverseNode(*commonAncestorContainer, 0, false /* embedded */);
409 if (_domRangeStartIndex > 0 && _domRangeStartIndex <= [_attrStr length])
410 [_attrStr deleteCharactersInRange:NSMakeRange(0, _domRangeStartIndex)];
411
412 return { WTFMove(_attrStr), WTFMove(_documentAttrs) };
413}

416// Returns the font to be used if the NSFontAttributeName doesn't exist
417static NSFont *WebDefaultFont()
418{
419 static auto defaultFont = makeNeverDestroyed([] {
420 NSFont *font = [NSFont fontWithName:@"Helvetica" size:12];
421 if (!font)
422 font = [NSFont systemFontOfSize:12];
423 return retainPtr(font);
424 }());
425 return defaultFont.get().get();
426}

429static PlatformFont *_fontForNameAndSize(NSString *fontName, CGFloat size, NSMutableDictionary *cache)
430{
431 PlatformFont *font = [cache objectForKey:fontName];
432#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
433 if (font)
434 return [font fontWithSize:size];
435
436 font = [PlatformFontClass fontWithName:fontName size:size];
437#else
438 NSFontManager *fontManager = [NSFontManager sharedFontManager];
439 if (font) {
440 font = [fontManager convertFont:font toSize:size];
441 return font;
442 }
443 font = [fontManager fontWithFamily:fontName traits:0 weight:0 size:size];
444#endif
445 if (!font) {
446#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
447 NSArray *availableFamilyNames = [PlatformFontClass familyNames];
448#else
449 NSArray *availableFamilyNames = [fontManager availableFontFamilies];
450#endif
451 NSRange dividingRange;
452 NSRange dividingSpaceRange = [fontName rangeOfString:@" " options:NSBackwardsSearch];
453 NSRange dividingDashRange = [fontName rangeOfString:@"-" options:NSBackwardsSearch];
454 dividingRange = (0 < dividingSpaceRange.length && 0 < dividingDashRange.length) ? (dividingSpaceRange.location > dividingDashRange.location ? dividingSpaceRange : dividingDashRange) : (0 < dividingSpaceRange.length ? dividingSpaceRange : dividingDashRange);
455
456 while (dividingRange.length > 0) {
457 NSString *familyName = [fontName substringToIndex:dividingRange.location];
458 if ([availableFamilyNames containsObject:familyName]) {
459#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
460 NSString *faceName = [fontName substringFromIndex:(dividingRange.location + dividingRange.length)];
461 NSArray *familyMemberFaceNames = [PlatformFontClass fontNamesForFamilyName:familyName];
462 for (NSString *familyMemberFaceName in familyMemberFaceNames) {
463 if ([familyMemberFaceName compare:faceName options:NSCaseInsensitiveSearch] == NSOrderedSame) {
464 font = [PlatformFontClass fontWithName:familyMemberFaceName size:size];
465 break;
466 }
467 }
468 if (!font && [familyMemberFaceNames count])
469 font = [PlatformFontClass fontWithName:familyName size:size];
470#else
471 NSArray *familyMemberArray;
472 NSString *faceName = [fontName substringFromIndex:(dividingRange.location + dividingRange.length)];
473 NSArray *familyMemberArrays = [fontManager availableMembersOfFontFamily:familyName];
474 NSEnumerator *familyMemberArraysEnum = [familyMemberArrays objectEnumerator];
475 while ((familyMemberArray = [familyMemberArraysEnum nextObject])) {
476 NSString *familyMemberFaceName = [familyMemberArray objectAtIndex:1];
477 if ([familyMemberFaceName compare:faceName options:NSCaseInsensitiveSearch] == NSOrderedSame) {
478 NSFontTraitMask traits = [[familyMemberArray objectAtIndex:3] integerValue];
479 NSInteger weight = [[familyMemberArray objectAtIndex:2] integerValue];
480 font = [fontManager fontWithFamily:familyName traits:traits weight:weight size:size];
481 break;
482 }
483 }
484 if (!font) {
485 if (0 < [familyMemberArrays count]) {
486 NSArray *familyMemberArray = [familyMemberArrays objectAtIndex:0];
487 NSFontTraitMask traits = [[familyMemberArray objectAtIndex:3] integerValue];
488 NSInteger weight = [[familyMemberArray objectAtIndex:2] integerValue];
489 font = [fontManager fontWithFamily:familyName traits:traits weight:weight size:size];
490 }
491 }
492#endif
493 break;
494 } else {
495 dividingSpaceRange = [familyName rangeOfString:@" " options:NSBackwardsSearch];
496 dividingDashRange = [familyName rangeOfString:@"-" options:NSBackwardsSearch];
497 dividingRange = (0 < dividingSpaceRange.length && 0 < dividingDashRange.length) ? (dividingSpaceRange.location > dividingDashRange.location ? dividingSpaceRange : dividingDashRange) : (0 < dividingSpaceRange.length ? dividingSpaceRange : dividingDashRange);
498 }
499 }
500 }
501#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
502 if (!font)
503 font = [PlatformFontClass systemFontOfSize:size];
504#else
505 if (!font)
506 font = [NSFont fontWithName:@"Times" size:size];
507 if (!font)
508 font = [NSFont userFontOfSize:size];
509 if (!font)
510 font = [fontManager convertFont:WebDefaultFont() toSize:size];
511 if (!font)
512 font = WebDefaultFont();
513#endif
514 [cache setObject:font forKey:fontName];
515
516 return font;
517}

530RefPtr<CSSValue> HTMLConverterCaches::computedStylePropertyForElement(Element& element, CSSPropertyID propertyId)
531{
532 if (propertyId == CSSPropertyInvalid)
533 return nullptr;
534
535 auto result = m_computedStyles.add(&element, nullptr);
536 if (result.isNewEntry)
537 result.iterator->value = makeUnique<ComputedStyleExtractor>(&element, true);
538 ComputedStyleExtractor& computedStyle = *result.iterator->value;
539 return computedStyle.propertyValue(propertyId);
540}
541
542RefPtr<CSSValue> HTMLConverterCaches::inlineStylePropertyForElement(Element& element, CSSPropertyID propertyId)
543{
544 if (propertyId == CSSPropertyInvalid || !is<StyledElement>(element))
545 return nullptr;
546 const StyleProperties* properties = downcast<StyledElement>(element).inlineStyle();
547 if (!properties)
548 return nullptr;
549 return properties->getPropertyCSSValue(propertyId);
550}
551
552static bool stringFromCSSValue(CSSValue& value, String& result)
553{
554 if (is<CSSPrimitiveValue>(value)) {
555 // FIXME: Use isStringType(CSSUnitType)?
556 CSSUnitType primitiveType = downcast<CSSPrimitiveValue>(value).primitiveType();
557 if (primitiveType == CSSUnitType::CSS_STRING || primitiveType == CSSUnitType::CSS_URI
558 || primitiveType == CSSUnitType::CSS_IDENT || primitiveType == CSSUnitType::CSS_ATTR) {
559 String stringValue = value.cssText();
560 if (stringValue.length()) {
561 result = stringValue;
562 return true;
563 }
564 }
565 } else if (value.isValueList()) {
566 result = value.cssText();
567 return true;
568 }
569 return false;
570}
571
572String HTMLConverterCaches::propertyValueForNode(Node& node, CSSPropertyID propertyId)
573{
574 if (!is<Element>(node)) {
575 if (Node* parent = node.parentInComposedTree())
576 return propertyValueForNode(*parent, propertyId);
577 return String();
578 }
579
580 bool inherit = false;
581 Element& element = downcast<Element>(node);
582 if (RefPtr<CSSValue> value = computedStylePropertyForElement(element, propertyId)) {
583 String result;
584 if (stringFromCSSValue(*value, result))
585 return result;
586 }
587
588 if (RefPtr<CSSValue> value = inlineStylePropertyForElement(element, propertyId)) {
589 String result;
590 if (value->isInheritedValue())
591 inherit = true;
592 else if (stringFromCSSValue(*value, result))
593 return result;
594 }
595
596 switch (propertyId) {
597 case CSSPropertyDisplay:
598 if (element.hasTagName(headTag) || element.hasTagName(scriptTag) || element.hasTagName(appletTag) || element.hasTagName(noframesTag))
599 return "none";
600 else if (element.hasTagName(addressTag) || element.hasTagName(blockquoteTag) || element.hasTagName(bodyTag) || element.hasTagName(centerTag)
601 || element.hasTagName(ddTag) || element.hasTagName(dirTag) || element.hasTagName(divTag) || element.hasTagName(dlTag)
602 || element.hasTagName(dtTag) || element.hasTagName(fieldsetTag) || element.hasTagName(formTag) || element.hasTagName(frameTag)
603 || element.hasTagName(framesetTag) || element.hasTagName(hrTag) || element.hasTagName(htmlTag) || element.hasTagName(h1Tag)
604 || element.hasTagName(h2Tag) || element.hasTagName(h3Tag) || element.hasTagName(h4Tag) || element.hasTagName(h5Tag)
605 || element.hasTagName(h6Tag) || element.hasTagName(iframeTag) || element.hasTagName(menuTag) || element.hasTagName(noscriptTag)
606 || element.hasTagName(olTag) || element.hasTagName(pTag) || element.hasTagName(preTag) || element.hasTagName(ulTag))
607 return "block";
608 else if (element.hasTagName(liTag))
609 return "list-item";
610 else if (element.hasTagName(tableTag))
611 return "table";
612 else if (element.hasTagName(trTag))
613 return "table-row";
614 else if (element.hasTagName(thTag) || element.hasTagName(tdTag))
615 return "table-cell";
616 else if (element.hasTagName(theadTag))
617 return "table-header-group";
618 else if (element.hasTagName(tbodyTag))
619 return "table-row-group";
620 else if (element.hasTagName(tfootTag))
621 return "table-footer-group";
622 else if (element.hasTagName(colTag))
623 return "table-column";
624 else if (element.hasTagName(colgroupTag))
625 return "table-column-group";
626 else if (element.hasTagName(captionTag))
627 return "table-caption";
628 break;
629 case CSSPropertyWhiteSpace:
630 if (element.hasTagName(preTag))
631 return "pre";
632 inherit = true;
633 break;
634 case CSSPropertyFontStyle:
635 if (element.hasTagName(iTag) || element.hasTagName(citeTag) || element.hasTagName(emTag) || element.hasTagName(varTag) || element.hasTagName(addressTag))
636 return "italic";
637 inherit = true;
638 break;
639 case CSSPropertyFontWeight:
640 if (element.hasTagName(bTag) || element.hasTagName(strongTag) || element.hasTagName(thTag))
641 return "bolder";
642 inherit = true;
643 break;
644 case CSSPropertyTextDecoration:
645 if (element.hasTagName(uTag) || element.hasTagName(insTag))
646 return "underline";
647 else if (element.hasTagName(sTag) || element.hasTagName(strikeTag) || element.hasTagName(delTag))
648 return "line-through";
649 inherit = true; // FIXME: This is not strictly correct
650 break;
651 case CSSPropertyTextAlign:
652 if (element.hasTagName(centerTag) || element.hasTagName(captionTag) || element.hasTagName(thTag))
653 return "center";
654 inherit = true;
655 break;
656 case CSSPropertyVerticalAlign:
657 if (element.hasTagName(supTag))
658 return "super";
659 else if (element.hasTagName(subTag))
660 return "sub";
661 else if (element.hasTagName(theadTag) || element.hasTagName(tbodyTag) || element.hasTagName(tfootTag))
662 return "middle";
663 else if (element.hasTagName(trTag) || element.hasTagName(thTag) || element.hasTagName(tdTag))
664 inherit = true;
665 break;
666 case CSSPropertyFontFamily:
667 case CSSPropertyFontVariantCaps:
668 case CSSPropertyTextTransform:
669 case CSSPropertyTextShadow:
670 case CSSPropertyVisibility:
671 case CSSPropertyBorderCollapse:
672 case CSSPropertyEmptyCells:
673 case CSSPropertyWordSpacing:
674 case CSSPropertyListStyleType:
675 case CSSPropertyDirection:
676 inherit = true; // FIXME: Let classes in the css component figure this out.
677 break;
678 default:
679 break;
680 }
681
682 if (inherit) {
683 if (Node* parent = node.parentInComposedTree())
684 return propertyValueForNode(*parent, propertyId);
685 }
686
687 return String();
688}
689
690static inline bool floatValueFromPrimitiveValue(CSSPrimitiveValue& primitiveValue, float& result)
691{
692 // FIXME: Use CSSPrimitiveValue::computeValue.
693 switch (primitiveValue.primitiveType()) {
694 case CSSUnitType::CSS_PX:
695 result = primitiveValue.floatValue(CSSUnitType::CSS_PX);
696 return true;
697 case CSSUnitType::CSS_PT:
698 result = 4 * primitiveValue.floatValue(CSSUnitType::CSS_PT) / 3;
699 return true;
700 case CSSUnitType::CSS_PC:
701 result = 16 * primitiveValue.floatValue(CSSUnitType::CSS_PC);
702 return true;
703 case CSSUnitType::CSS_CM:
704 result = 96 * primitiveValue.floatValue(CSSUnitType::CSS_PC) / 2.54;
705 return true;
706 case CSSUnitType::CSS_MM:
707 result = 96 * primitiveValue.floatValue(CSSUnitType::CSS_PC) / 25.4;
708 return true;
709 case CSSUnitType::CSS_Q:
710 result = 96 * primitiveValue.floatValue(CSSUnitType::CSS_PC) / (25.4 * 4.0);
711 return true;
712 case CSSUnitType::CSS_IN:
713 result = 96 * primitiveValue.floatValue(CSSUnitType::CSS_IN);
714 return true;
715 default:
716 return false;
717 }
718}
719
720bool HTMLConverterCaches::floatPropertyValueForNode(Node& node, CSSPropertyID propertyId, float& result)
721{
722 if (!is<Element>(node)) {
723 if (ContainerNode* parent = node.parentInComposedTree())
724 return floatPropertyValueForNode(*parent, propertyId, result);
725 return false;
726 }
727
728 Element& element = downcast<Element>(node);
729 if (RefPtr<CSSValue> value = computedStylePropertyForElement(element, propertyId)) {
730 if (is<CSSPrimitiveValue>(*value) && floatValueFromPrimitiveValue(downcast<CSSPrimitiveValue>(*value), result))
731 return true;
732 }
733
734 bool inherit = false;
735 if (RefPtr<CSSValue> value = inlineStylePropertyForElement(element, propertyId)) {
736 if (is<CSSPrimitiveValue>(*value) && floatValueFromPrimitiveValue(downcast<CSSPrimitiveValue>(*value), result))
737 return true;
738 if (value->isInheritedValue())
739 inherit = true;
740 }
741
742 switch (propertyId) {
743 case CSSPropertyTextIndent:
744 case CSSPropertyLetterSpacing:
745 case CSSPropertyWordSpacing:
746 case CSSPropertyLineHeight:
747 case CSSPropertyWidows:
748 case CSSPropertyOrphans:
749 inherit = true;
750 break;
751 default:
752 break;
753 }
754
755 if (inherit) {
756 if (ContainerNode* parent = node.parentInComposedTree())
757 return floatPropertyValueForNode(*parent, propertyId, result);
758 }
759
760 return false;
761}

763static inline NSShadow *_shadowForShadowStyle(NSString *shadowStyle)
764{
765 RetainPtr<NSShadow> shadow;
766 NSUInteger shadowStyleLength = [shadowStyle length];
767 NSRange openParenRange = [shadowStyle rangeOfString:@"("];
768 NSRange closeParenRange = [shadowStyle rangeOfString:@")"];
769 NSRange firstRange = NSMakeRange(NSNotFound, 0);
770 NSRange secondRange = NSMakeRange(NSNotFound, 0);
771 NSRange thirdRange = NSMakeRange(NSNotFound, 0);
772 NSRange spaceRange;
773 if (openParenRange.length > 0 && closeParenRange.length > 0 && NSMaxRange(openParenRange) < closeParenRange.location) {
774 NSArray *components = [[shadowStyle substringWithRange:NSMakeRange(NSMaxRange(openParenRange), closeParenRange.location - NSMaxRange(openParenRange))] componentsSeparatedByString:@","];
775 if ([components count] >= 3) {
776 CGFloat red = [[components objectAtIndex:0] floatValue] / 255;
777 CGFloat green = [[components objectAtIndex:1] floatValue] / 255;
778 CGFloat blue = [[components objectAtIndex:2] floatValue] / 255;
779 CGFloat alpha = ([components count] >= 4) ? [[components objectAtIndex:3] floatValue] / 255 : 1;
780 NSColor *shadowColor = [PlatformNSColorClass colorWithCalibratedRed:red green:green blue:blue alpha:alpha];
781 NSSize shadowOffset;
782 CGFloat shadowBlurRadius;
783 firstRange = [shadowStyle rangeOfString:@"px"];
784 if (firstRange.length > 0 && NSMaxRange(firstRange) < shadowStyleLength)
785 secondRange = [shadowStyle rangeOfString:@"px" options:0 range:NSMakeRange(NSMaxRange(firstRange), shadowStyleLength - NSMaxRange(firstRange))];
786 if (secondRange.length > 0 && NSMaxRange(secondRange) < shadowStyleLength)
787 thirdRange = [shadowStyle rangeOfString:@"px" options:0 range:NSMakeRange(NSMaxRange(secondRange), shadowStyleLength - NSMaxRange(secondRange))];
788 if (firstRange.location > 0 && firstRange.length > 0 && secondRange.length > 0 && thirdRange.length > 0) {
789 spaceRange = [shadowStyle rangeOfString:@" " options:NSBackwardsSearch range:NSMakeRange(0, firstRange.location)];
790 if (spaceRange.length == 0)
791 spaceRange = NSMakeRange(0, 0);
792 shadowOffset.width = [[shadowStyle substringWithRange:NSMakeRange(NSMaxRange(spaceRange), firstRange.location - NSMaxRange(spaceRange))] floatValue];
793 spaceRange = [shadowStyle rangeOfString:@" " options:NSBackwardsSearch range:NSMakeRange(0, secondRange.location)];
794 if (!spaceRange.length)
795 spaceRange = NSMakeRange(0, 0);
796 CGFloat shadowHeight = [[shadowStyle substringWithRange:NSMakeRange(NSMaxRange(spaceRange), secondRange.location - NSMaxRange(spaceRange))] floatValue];
797 // I don't know why we have this difference between the two platforms.
798#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
799 shadowOffset.height = shadowHeight;
800#else
801 shadowOffset.height = -shadowHeight;
802#endif
803 spaceRange = [shadowStyle rangeOfString:@" " options:NSBackwardsSearch range:NSMakeRange(0, thirdRange.location)];
804 if (!spaceRange.length)
805 spaceRange = NSMakeRange(0, 0);
806 shadowBlurRadius = [[shadowStyle substringWithRange:NSMakeRange(NSMaxRange(spaceRange), thirdRange.location - NSMaxRange(spaceRange))] floatValue];
807 shadow = adoptNS([(NSShadow *)[PlatformNSShadow alloc] init]);
808 [shadow setShadowColor:shadowColor];
809 [shadow setShadowOffset:shadowOffset];
810 [shadow setShadowBlurRadius:shadowBlurRadius];
811 }
812 }
813 }
814 return shadow.autorelease();
815}

817bool HTMLConverterCaches::isBlockElement(Element& element)
818{
819 String displayValue = propertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyDisplay);
820 if (displayValue == "block" || displayValue == "list-item" || displayValue.startsWith("table"))
821 return true;
822 String floatValue = propertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyFloat);
823 if (floatValue == "left" || floatValue == "right")
824 return true;
825 return false;
826}
827
828bool HTMLConverterCaches::elementHasOwnBackgroundColor(Element& element)
829{
830 if (!isBlockElement(element))
831 return false;
832 // In the text system, text blocks (table elements) and documents (body elements)
833 // have their own background colors, which should not be inherited.
834 return element.hasTagName(htmlTag) || element.hasTagName(bodyTag) || propertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyDisplay).startsWith("table");
835}

838{
839 Element* element = node->parentElement();
840 if (element && !_caches->isBlockElement(*element))
841 element = _blockLevelElementForNode(element->parentInComposedTree());

844
845static Color normalizedColor(Color color, bool ignoreDefaultColor, Element& element)
846{
847 if (!ignoreDefaultColor)
848 return color;
849
850 bool useDarkAppearance = element.document().useDarkAppearance(element.existingComputedStyle());
851 if (useDarkAppearance && Color::isWhiteColor(color))
852 return Color();
853
854 if (!useDarkAppearance && Color::isBlackColor(color))
855 return Color();
856
857 return color;
858}
859
860Color HTMLConverterCaches::colorPropertyValueForNode(Node& node, CSSPropertyID propertyId)
861{
862 if (!is<Element>(node)) {
863 if (Node* parent = node.parentInComposedTree())
864 return colorPropertyValueForNode(*parent, propertyId);
865 return Color();
866 }
867
868 bool ignoreDefaultColor = propertyId == CSSPropertyColor;
869
870 Element& element = downcast<Element>(node);
871 if (RefPtr<CSSValue> value = computedStylePropertyForElement(element, propertyId)) {
872 if (is<CSSPrimitiveValue>(*value) && downcast<CSSPrimitiveValue>(*value).isRGBColor())
873 return normalizedColor(downcast<CSSPrimitiveValue>(*value).color(), ignoreDefaultColor, element);
874 }
875
876 bool inherit = false;
877 if (RefPtr<CSSValue> value = inlineStylePropertyForElement(element, propertyId)) {
878 if (is<CSSPrimitiveValue>(*value) && downcast<CSSPrimitiveValue>(*value).isRGBColor())
879 return normalizedColor(downcast<CSSPrimitiveValue>(*value).color(), ignoreDefaultColor, element);
880 if (value->isInheritedValue())
881 inherit = true;
882 }
883
884 switch (propertyId) {
885 case CSSPropertyColor:
886 inherit = true;
887 break;
888 case CSSPropertyBackgroundColor:
889 if (!elementHasOwnBackgroundColor(element)) {
890 if (Element* parentElement = node.parentElement()) {
891 if (!elementHasOwnBackgroundColor(*parentElement))
892 inherit = true;
893 }
894 }
895 break;
896 default:
897 break;
898 }
899
900 if (inherit) {
901 if (Node* parent = node.parentInComposedTree())
902 return colorPropertyValueForNode(*parent, propertyId);
903 }
904
905 return Color();
906}
907
908PlatformColor *HTMLConverter::_colorForElement(Element& element, CSSPropertyID propertyId)
909{
910 Color result = _caches->colorPropertyValueForNode(element, propertyId);
911 if (!result.isValid())
912 return nil;
913 PlatformColor *platformResult = platformColor(result);
914 if ([[PlatformColorClass clearColor] isEqual:platformResult] || ([platformResult alphaComponent] == 0.0))
915 return nil;
916 return platformResult;
917}

926
927NSDictionary *HTMLConverter::computedAttributesForElement(Element& element)
928{
929 NSMutableDictionary *attrs = [NSMutableDictionary dictionary];
930#if !PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
931 NSFontManager *fontManager = [NSFontManager sharedFontManager];
932#endif
933
934 PlatformFont *font = nil;
935 PlatformFont *actualFont = _font(element);
936 PlatformColor *foregroundColor = _colorForElement(element, CSSPropertyColor);
937 PlatformColor *backgroundColor = _colorForElement(element, CSSPropertyBackgroundColor);
938 PlatformColor *strokeColor = _colorForElement(element, CSSPropertyWebkitTextStrokeColor);
939
940 float fontSize = 0;
941 if (!_caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyFontSize, fontSize) || fontSize <= 0.0)
942 fontSize = defaultFontSize;
943 if (fontSize < minimumFontSize)
944 fontSize = minimumFontSize;
945 if (fabs(floor(2.0 * fontSize + 0.5) / 2.0 - fontSize) < 0.05)
946 fontSize = floor(2.0 * fontSize + 0.5) / 2;
947 else if (fabs(floor(10.0 * fontSize + 0.5) / 10.0 - fontSize) < 0.005)
948 fontSize = floor(10.0 * fontSize + 0.5) / 10;
949
950 if (fontSize <= 0.0)
951 fontSize = defaultFontSize;
952
953#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
954 if (actualFont)
955 font = [actualFont fontWithSize:fontSize];
956#else
957 if (actualFont)
958 font = [fontManager convertFont:actualFont toSize:fontSize];
959#endif
960 if (!font) {
961 String fontName = _caches->propertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyFontFamily);
962 if (fontName.length())
963 font = _fontForNameAndSize(fontName.convertToASCIILowercase(), fontSize, _fontCache.get());
964 if (!font)
965 font = [PlatformFontClass fontWithName:@"Times" size:fontSize];
966
967 String fontStyle = _caches->propertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyFontStyle);
968 if (fontStyle == "italic" || fontStyle == "oblique") {
969 PlatformFont *originalFont = font;
970#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
971 font = [PlatformFontClass fontWithFamilyName:[font familyName] traits:UIFontTraitItalic size:[font pointSize]];
972#else
973 font = [fontManager convertFont:font toHaveTrait:NSItalicFontMask];
974#endif
975 if (!font)
976 font = originalFont;
977 }
978
979 String fontWeight = _caches->propertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyFontStyle);
980 if (fontWeight.startsWith("bold") || parseIntegerAllowingTrailingJunk<int>(fontWeight).value_or(0) >= 700) {
981 // ??? handle weight properly using NSFontManager
982 PlatformFont *originalFont = font;
983#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
984 font = [PlatformFontClass fontWithFamilyName:[font familyName] traits:UIFontTraitBold size:[font pointSize]];
985#else
986 font = [fontManager convertFont:font toHaveTrait:NSBoldFontMask];
987#endif
988 if (!font)
989 font = originalFont;
990 }
991#if !PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY) // IJB: No small caps support on iOS
992 if (_caches->propertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyFontVariantCaps) == "small-caps") {
993 // ??? synthesize small-caps if [font isEqual:originalFont]
994 NSFont *originalFont = font;
995 font = [fontManager convertFont:font toHaveTrait:NSSmallCapsFontMask];
996 if (!font)
997 font = originalFont;
998 }
999#endif
1000 }
1001 if (font)
1002 [attrs setObject:font forKey:NSFontAttributeName];
1003 if (foregroundColor)
1004 [attrs setObject:foregroundColor forKey:NSForegroundColorAttributeName];
1005 if (backgroundColor && !_caches->elementHasOwnBackgroundColor(element))
1006 [attrs setObject:backgroundColor forKey:NSBackgroundColorAttributeName];
1007
1008 float strokeWidth = 0.0;
1009 if (_caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyWebkitTextStrokeWidth, strokeWidth)) {
1010 float textStrokeWidth = strokeWidth / ([font pointSize] * 0.01);
1011 [attrs setObject:@(textStrokeWidth) forKey:NSStrokeWidthAttributeName];
1012 }
1013 if (strokeColor)
1014 [attrs setObject:strokeColor forKey:NSStrokeColorAttributeName];
1015
1016 String fontKerning = _caches->propertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyWebkitFontKerning);
1017 String letterSpacing = _caches->propertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyLetterSpacing);
1018 if (fontKerning.length() || letterSpacing.length()) {
1019 if (fontKerning == "none")
1020 [attrs setObject:@0.0 forKey:NSKernAttributeName];
1021 else {
1022 double kernVal = letterSpacing.length() ? letterSpacing.toDouble() : 0.0;
1023 if (fabs(kernVal - 0) < FLT_EPSILON)
1024 [attrs setObject:@0.0 forKey:NSKernAttributeName]; // auto and normal, the other possible values, are both "kerning enabled"
1025 else
1026 [attrs setObject:@(kernVal) forKey:NSKernAttributeName];
1027 }
1028 }
1029
1030 String fontLigatures = _caches->propertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyFontVariantLigatures);
1031 if (fontLigatures.length()) {
1032 if (fontLigatures.contains("normal"))
1033 ; // default: whatever the system decides to do
1034 else if (fontLigatures.contains("common-ligatures"))
1035 [attrs setObject:@1 forKey:NSLigatureAttributeName]; // explicitly enabled
1036 else if (fontLigatures.contains("no-common-ligatures"))
1037 [attrs setObject:@0 forKey:NSLigatureAttributeName]; // explicitly disabled
1038 }
1039
1040 String textDecoration = _caches->propertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyTextDecoration);
1041 if (textDecoration.length()) {
1042 if (textDecoration.contains("underline"))
1043 [attrs setObject:[NSNumber numberWithInteger:NSUnderlineStyleSingle] forKey:NSUnderlineStyleAttributeName];
1044 if (textDecoration.contains("line-through"))
1045 [attrs setObject:[NSNumber numberWithInteger:NSUnderlineStyleSingle] forKey:NSStrikethroughStyleAttributeName];
1046 }
1047
1048 String verticalAlign = _caches->propertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyVerticalAlign);
1049 if (verticalAlign.length()) {
1050 if (verticalAlign == "super")
1051 [attrs setObject:[NSNumber numberWithInteger:1] forKey:NSSuperscriptAttributeName];
1052 else if (verticalAlign == "sub")
1053 [attrs setObject:[NSNumber numberWithInteger:-1] forKey:NSSuperscriptAttributeName];
1054 }
1055
1056 float baselineOffset = 0.0;
1057 if (_caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyVerticalAlign, baselineOffset))
1058 [attrs setObject:@(baselineOffset) forKey:NSBaselineOffsetAttributeName];
1059
1060 String textShadow = _caches->propertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyTextShadow);
1061 if (textShadow.length() > 4) {
1062 NSShadow *shadow = _shadowForShadowStyle(textShadow);
1063 if (shadow)
1064 [attrs setObject:shadow forKey:NSShadowAttributeName];
1065 }
1066
1067 Element* blockElement = _blockLevelElementForNode(&element);
1068 if (&element != blockElement && [_writingDirectionArray count] > 0)
1069 [attrs setObject:[NSArray arrayWithArray:_writingDirectionArray.get()] forKey:NSWritingDirectionAttributeName];
1070
1071 if (blockElement) {
1072 Element& coreBlockElement = *blockElement;
1073 RetainPtr<NSMutableParagraphStyle> paragraphStyle = adoptNS([defaultParagraphStyle() mutableCopy]);
1074 unsigned heading = 0;
1075 if (coreBlockElement.hasTagName(h1Tag))
1076 heading = 1;
1077 else if (coreBlockElement.hasTagName(h2Tag))
1078 heading = 2;
1079 else if (coreBlockElement.hasTagName(h3Tag))
1080 heading = 3;
1081 else if (coreBlockElement.hasTagName(h4Tag))
1082 heading = 4;
1083 else if (coreBlockElement.hasTagName(h5Tag))
1084 heading = 5;
1085 else if (coreBlockElement.hasTagName(h6Tag))
1086 heading = 6;
1087 bool isParagraph = coreBlockElement.hasTagName(pTag) || coreBlockElement.hasTagName(liTag) || heading;
1088
1089 String textAlign = _caches->propertyValueForNode(coreBlockElement, CSSPropertyTextAlign);
1090 if (textAlign.length()) {
1091 // WebKit can return -khtml-left, -khtml-right, -khtml-center
1092 if (textAlign.endsWith("left"))
1093 [paragraphStyle setAlignment:NSTextAlignmentLeft];
1094 else if (textAlign.endsWith("right"))
1095 [paragraphStyle setAlignment:NSTextAlignmentRight];
1096 else if (textAlign.endsWith("center"))
1097 [paragraphStyle setAlignment:NSTextAlignmentCenter];
1098 else if (textAlign.endsWith("justify"))
1099 [paragraphStyle setAlignment:NSTextAlignmentJustified];
1100 }
1101
1102 String direction = _caches->propertyValueForNode(coreBlockElement, CSSPropertyDirection);
1103 if (direction.length()) {
1104 if (direction == "ltr")
1105 [paragraphStyle setBaseWritingDirection:NSWritingDirectionLeftToRight];
1106 else if (direction == "rtl")
1107 [paragraphStyle setBaseWritingDirection:NSWritingDirectionRightToLeft];
1108 }
1109
1110 String hyphenation = _caches->propertyValueForNode(coreBlockElement, CSSPropertyWebkitHyphens);
1111 if (hyphenation.length()) {
1112 if (hyphenation == "auto")
1113 [paragraphStyle setHyphenationFactor:1.0];
1114 else
1115 [paragraphStyle setHyphenationFactor:0.0];
1116 }
1117 if (heading)
1118 [paragraphStyle setHeaderLevel:heading];
1119 if (isParagraph) {
1120 // FIXME: Why are we ignoring margin-top?
1121 float marginLeft = 0.0;
1122 if (_caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(coreBlockElement, CSSPropertyMarginLeft, marginLeft) && marginLeft > 0.0)
1123 [paragraphStyle setHeadIndent:marginLeft];
1124 float textIndent = 0.0;
1125 if (_caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(coreBlockElement, CSSPropertyTextIndent, textIndent) && textIndent > 0.0)
1126 [paragraphStyle setFirstLineHeadIndent:[paragraphStyle headIndent] + textIndent];
1127 float marginRight = 0.0;
1128 if (_caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(coreBlockElement, CSSPropertyMarginRight, marginRight) && marginRight > 0.0)
1129 [paragraphStyle setTailIndent:-marginRight];
1130 float marginBottom = 0.0;
1131 if (_caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(coreBlockElement, CSSPropertyMarginRight, marginBottom) && marginBottom > 0.0)
1132 [paragraphStyle setParagraphSpacing:marginBottom];
1133 }
1134 if ([_textLists count] > 0)
1135 [paragraphStyle setTextLists:_textLists.get()];
1136 if ([_textBlocks count] > 0)
1137 [paragraphStyle setTextBlocks:_textBlocks.get()];
1138 [attrs setObject:paragraphStyle.get() forKey:NSParagraphStyleAttributeName];
1139 }
1140 return attrs;
1141}

1144NSDictionary* HTMLConverter::attributesForElement(Element& element)
1145{
1146 auto& attributes = m_attributesForElements.add(&element, nullptr).iterator->value;
1147 if (!attributes)
1148 attributes = computedAttributesForElement(element);
1149 return attributes.get();

1151
1152NSDictionary* HTMLConverter::aggregatedAttributesForAncestors(CharacterData& node)
1153{
1154 Node* ancestor = node.parentInComposedTree();
1155 while (ancestor && !is<Element>(*ancestor))
1156 ancestor = ancestor->parentInComposedTree();
1157 if (!ancestor)
1158 return nullptr;
1159 return aggregatedAttributesForElementAndItsAncestors(downcast<Element>(*ancestor));
1160}
1161
1162NSDictionary* HTMLConverter::aggregatedAttributesForElementAndItsAncestors(Element& element)
1163{
1164 auto& cachedAttributes = m_aggregatedAttributesForElements.add(&element, nullptr).iterator->value;
1165 if (cachedAttributes)
1166 return cachedAttributes.get();
1167
1168 NSDictionary* attributesForCurrentElement = attributesForElement(element);
1169 ASSERT(attributesForCurrentElement);
1170
1171 Node* ancestor = element.parentInComposedTree();
1172 while (ancestor && !is<Element>(*ancestor))
1173 ancestor = ancestor->parentInComposedTree();
1174
1175 if (!ancestor) {
1176 cachedAttributes = attributesForCurrentElement;
1177 return attributesForCurrentElement;
1178 }
1179
1180 RetainPtr<NSMutableDictionary> attributesForAncestors = adoptNS([aggregatedAttributesForElementAndItsAncestors(downcast<Element>(*ancestor)) mutableCopy]);
1181 [attributesForAncestors addEntriesFromDictionary:attributesForCurrentElement];
1182 m_aggregatedAttributesForElements.set(&element, attributesForAncestors);
1183
1184 return attributesForAncestors.get();
1185}
1186
1187void HTMLConverter::_newParagraphForElement(Element& element, NSString *tag, BOOL flag, BOOL suppressTrailingSpace)
1188{
1189 NSUInteger textLength = [_attrStr length];
1190 unichar lastChar = (textLength > 0) ? [[_attrStr string] characterAtIndex:textLength - 1] : '\n';
1191 NSRange rangeToReplace = (suppressTrailingSpace && _flags.isSoft && (lastChar == ' ' || lastChar == NSLineSeparatorCharacter)) ? NSMakeRange(textLength - 1, 1) : NSMakeRange(textLength, 0);
1192 BOOL needBreak = (flag || lastChar != '\n');
1193 if (needBreak) {
1194 NSString *string = (([@"BODY" isEqualToString:tag] || [@"HTML" isEqualToString:tag]) ? @"" : @"\n");
1195 [_writingDirectionArray removeAllObjects];
1196 [_attrStr replaceCharactersInRange:rangeToReplace withString:string];
1197 if (rangeToReplace.location < _domRangeStartIndex)
1198 _domRangeStartIndex += [string length] - rangeToReplace.length;
1199 rangeToReplace.length = [string length];
1200 NSDictionary *attrs = attributesForElement(element);
1201 if (rangeToReplace.length > 0)
1202 [_attrStr setAttributes:attrs range:rangeToReplace];
1203 _flags.isSoft = YES;
1204 }
1205}
1206
1207void HTMLConverter::_newLineForElement(Element& element)
1208{
1209 unichar c = NSLineSeparatorCharacter;
1210 RetainPtr<NSString> string = adoptNS([[NSString alloc] initWithCharacters:&c length:1]);
1211 NSUInteger textLength = [_attrStr length];
1212 NSRange rangeToReplace = NSMakeRange(textLength, 0);
1213 [_attrStr replaceCharactersInRange:rangeToReplace withString:string.get()];
1214 rangeToReplace.length = [string length];
1215 if (rangeToReplace.location < _domRangeStartIndex)
1216 _domRangeStartIndex += rangeToReplace.length;
1217 NSDictionary *attrs = attributesForElement(element);
1218 if (rangeToReplace.length > 0)
1219 [_attrStr setAttributes:attrs range:rangeToReplace];
1220 _flags.isSoft = YES;
1221}

1223void HTMLConverter::_newTabForElement(Element& element)
1224{
1225 NSString *string = @"\t";

1227 unichar lastChar = (textLength > 0) ? [[_attrStr string] characterAtIndex:textLength - 1] : '\n';
1228 NSRange rangeToReplace = (_flags.isSoft && lastChar == ' ') ? NSMakeRange(textLength - 1, 1) : NSMakeRange(textLength, 0);
1229 [_attrStr replaceCharactersInRange:rangeToReplace withString:string];
1230 rangeToReplace.length = [string length];
1231 if (rangeToReplace.location < _domRangeStartIndex)
1232 _domRangeStartIndex += rangeToReplace.length;
1233 NSDictionary *attrs = attributesForElement(element);
1234 if (rangeToReplace.length > 0)

1236 _flags.isSoft = YES;

1240{

1258BOOL HTMLConverter::_addAttachmentForElement(Element& element, NSURL *url, BOOL needsParagraph, BOOL usePlaceholder)
1259{
1260 BOOL retval = NO;
1261 BOOL notFound = NO;
1262 RetainPtr<NSFileWrapper> fileWrapper;
1263 Frame* frame = element.document().frame();
1264 DocumentLoader *dataSource = frame->loader().frameHasLoaded() ? frame->loader().documentLoader() : 0;
1265 BOOL ignoreOrientation = YES;
1266
1267 if ([url isFileURL]) {
1268 NSString *path = [[url path] stringByStandardizingPath];
1269 if (path)
1270 fileWrapper = adoptNS([[NSFileWrapper alloc] initWithURL:url options:0 error:NULL]);
1271 }
1272 if (!fileWrapper && dataSource) {
1273 if (auto resource = dataSource->subresource(url)) {
1274 auto& mimeType = resource->mimeType();
1275 if (!usePlaceholder || mimeType != "text/html") {
1276 fileWrapper = adoptNS([[NSFileWrapper alloc] initRegularFileWithContents:resource->data().createNSData().get()]);
1277 [fileWrapper setPreferredFilename:suggestedFilenameWithMIMEType(url, mimeType)];
1278 } else
1279 notFound = YES;
1280 }
1281 }
1282#if !PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
1283 if (!fileWrapper && !notFound) {
1284 fileWrapper = fileWrapperForURL(dataSource, url);
1285 if (usePlaceholder && fileWrapper && [[[[fileWrapper preferredFilename] pathExtension] lowercaseString] hasPrefix:@"htm"])
1286 notFound = YES;
1287 if (notFound)
1288 fileWrapper = nil;
1289 }
1290 if (!fileWrapper && !notFound) {
1291 fileWrapper = fileWrapperForURL(m_dataSource, url);
1292 if (usePlaceholder && fileWrapper && [[[[fileWrapper preferredFilename] pathExtension] lowercaseString] hasPrefix:@"htm"])
1293 notFound = YES;
1294 if (notFound)
1295 fileWrapper = nil;
1296 }
1297#endif
1298 if (!fileWrapper && !notFound && url) {
1299 // Special handling for Mail attachments, until WebKit provides a standard way to get the data.
1300 Class WebMessageDocumentClass = _WebMessageDocumentClass();
1301 if (WebMessageDocumentClass) {
1302 NSTextAttachment *mimeTextAttachment = nil;
1303 [WebMessageDocumentClass document:NULL attachment:&mimeTextAttachment forURL:url];
1304 if (mimeTextAttachment && [mimeTextAttachment respondsToSelector:@selector(fileWrapper)]) {
1305 fileWrapper = [mimeTextAttachment performSelector:@selector(fileWrapper)];
1306 ignoreOrientation = NO;
1307 }
1308 }
1309 }
1310 if (fileWrapper || usePlaceholder) {
1311 NSUInteger textLength = [_attrStr length];
1312 RetainPtr<NSTextAttachment> attachment = adoptNS([[PlatformNSTextAttachment alloc] initWithFileWrapper:fileWrapper.get()]);
1313#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
1314 float verticalAlign = 0.0;
1315 _caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyVerticalAlign, verticalAlign);
1316 attachment.get().bounds = CGRectMake(0, (verticalAlign / 100) * element.clientHeight(), element.clientWidth(), element.clientHeight());
1317#endif
1318 RetainPtr<NSString> string = adoptNS([[NSString alloc] initWithFormat:(needsParagraph ? @"%C\n" : @"%C"), static_cast<unichar>(NSAttachmentCharacter)]);
1319 NSRange rangeToReplace = NSMakeRange(textLength, 0);
1320 NSDictionary *attrs;
1321 if (fileWrapper) {
1322#if !PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
1323 if (ignoreOrientation)
1324 [attachment setIgnoresOrientation:YES];
1325#endif
1326 } else {
1327 NSBundle *webCoreBundle = [NSBundle bundleWithIdentifier:@"com.apple.WebCore"];
1328#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
1329 UIImage *missingImage = [PlatformImageClass imageNamed:@"missingImage" inBundle:webCoreBundle compatibleWithTraitCollection:nil];
1330#else
1331 NSImage *missingImage = [webCoreBundle imageForResource:@"missingImage"];
1332#endif
1333 ASSERT_WITH_MESSAGE(missingImage != nil, "Unable to find missingImage.");
1334 attachment = adoptNS([[PlatformNSTextAttachment alloc] initWithData:nil ofType:nil]);
1335 attachment.get().image = missingImage;
1336 }
1337 [_attrStr replaceCharactersInRange:rangeToReplace withString:string.get()];
1338 rangeToReplace.length = [string length];
1339 if (rangeToReplace.location < _domRangeStartIndex)
1340 _domRangeStartIndex += rangeToReplace.length;
1341 attrs = attributesForElement(element);
1342 if (rangeToReplace.length > 0) {
1343 [_attrStr setAttributes:attrs range:rangeToReplace];
1344 rangeToReplace.length = 1;
1345 [_attrStr addAttribute:NSAttachmentAttributeName value:attachment.get() range:rangeToReplace];
1346 }
1347 _flags.isSoft = NO;
1348 retval = YES;
1349 }
1350 return retval;
1351}

1386void HTMLConverter::_fillInBlock(NSTextBlock *block, Element& element, PlatformColor *backgroundColor, CGFloat extraMargin, CGFloat extraPadding, BOOL isTable)
1387{
1388 float result = 0;
1389
1390 NSString *width = element.getAttribute(widthAttr);
1391 if ((width && [width length]) || !isTable) {
1392 if (_caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyWidth, result))
1393 [block setValue:result type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forDimension:NSTextBlockWidth];
1394 }
1395
1396 if (_caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyMinWidth, result))
1397 [block setValue:result type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forDimension:NSTextBlockMinimumWidth];
1398 if (_caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyMaxWidth, result))
1399 [block setValue:result type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forDimension:NSTextBlockMaximumWidth];
1400 if (_caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyMinHeight, result))
1401 [block setValue:result type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forDimension:NSTextBlockMinimumHeight];
1402 if (_caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyMaxHeight, result))
1403 [block setValue:result type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forDimension:NSTextBlockMaximumHeight];
1404
1405 if (_caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyPaddingLeft, result))
1406 [block setWidth:result + extraPadding type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forLayer:NSTextBlockPadding edge:NSMinXEdge];
1407 else
1408 [block setWidth:extraPadding type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forLayer:NSTextBlockPadding edge:NSMinXEdge];
1409
1410 if (_caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyPaddingTop, result))
1411 [block setWidth:result + extraPadding type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forLayer:NSTextBlockPadding edge:NSMinYEdge];
1412 else
1413 [block setWidth:extraPadding type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forLayer:NSTextBlockPadding edge:NSMinYEdge];
1414
1415 if (_caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyPaddingRight, result))
1416 [block setWidth:result + extraPadding type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forLayer:NSTextBlockPadding edge:NSMaxXEdge];
1417 else
1418 [block setWidth:extraPadding type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forLayer:NSTextBlockPadding edge:NSMaxXEdge];
1419
1420 if (_caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyPaddingBottom, result))
1421 [block setWidth:result + extraPadding type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forLayer:NSTextBlockPadding edge:NSMaxYEdge];
1422 else
1423 [block setWidth:extraPadding type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forLayer:NSTextBlockPadding edge:NSMaxYEdge];
1424
1425 if (_caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyBorderLeftWidth, result))
1426 [block setWidth:result type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forLayer:NSTextBlockBorder edge:NSMinXEdge];
1427 if (_caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyBorderTopWidth, result))
1428 [block setWidth:result type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forLayer:NSTextBlockBorder edge:NSMinYEdge];
1429 if (_caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyBorderRightWidth, result))
1430 [block setWidth:result type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forLayer:NSTextBlockBorder edge:NSMaxXEdge];
1431 if (_caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyBorderBottomWidth, result))
1432 [block setWidth:result type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forLayer:NSTextBlockBorder edge:NSMaxYEdge];
1433
1434 if (_caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyMarginLeft, result))
1435 [block setWidth:result + extraMargin type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forLayer:NSTextBlockMargin edge:NSMinXEdge];
1436 else
1437 [block setWidth:extraMargin type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forLayer:NSTextBlockMargin edge:NSMinXEdge];
1438 if (_caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyMarginTop, result))
1439 [block setWidth:result + extraMargin type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forLayer:NSTextBlockMargin edge:NSMinYEdge];
1440 else
1441 [block setWidth:extraMargin type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forLayer:NSTextBlockMargin edge:NSMinYEdge];
1442 if (_caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyMarginRight, result))
1443 [block setWidth:result + extraMargin type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forLayer:NSTextBlockMargin edge:NSMaxXEdge];
1444 else
1445 [block setWidth:extraMargin type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forLayer:NSTextBlockMargin edge:NSMaxXEdge];
1446 if (_caches->floatPropertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyMarginBottom, result))
1447 [block setWidth:result + extraMargin type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forLayer:NSTextBlockMargin edge:NSMaxYEdge];
1448 else
1449 [block setWidth:extraMargin type:NSTextBlockAbsoluteValueType forLayer:NSTextBlockMargin edge:NSMaxYEdge];
1450
1451 PlatformColor *color = nil;
1452 if ((color = _colorForElement(element, CSSPropertyBackgroundColor)))
1453 [block setBackgroundColor:color];
1454 if (!color && backgroundColor)
1455 [block setBackgroundColor:backgroundColor];
1456
1457 if ((color = _colorForElement(element, CSSPropertyBorderLeftColor)))
1458 [block setBorderColor:color forEdge:NSMinXEdge];
1459
1460 if ((color = _colorForElement(element, CSSPropertyBorderTopColor)))
1461 [block setBorderColor:color forEdge:NSMinYEdge];
1462 if ((color = _colorForElement(element, CSSPropertyBorderRightColor)))
1463 [block setBorderColor:color forEdge:NSMaxXEdge];
1464 if ((color = _colorForElement(element, CSSPropertyBorderBottomColor)))
1465 [block setBorderColor:color forEdge:NSMaxYEdge];
1466}

1468static inline BOOL read2DigitNumber(const char **pp, int8_t *outval)
1469{
1470 BOOL result = NO;
1471 char c1 = *(*pp)++, c2;
1472 if (isASCIIDigit(c1)) {
1473 c2 = *(*pp)++;
1474 if (isASCIIDigit(c2)) {
1475 *outval = 10 * (c1 - '0') + (c2 - '0');
1476 result = YES;
1477 }
1478 }
1479 return result;
1480}
1481
1482static inline NSDate *_dateForString(NSString *string)
1483{
1484 const char *p = [string UTF8String];
1485 RetainPtr<NSDateComponents> dateComponents = adoptNS([[NSDateComponents alloc] init]);
1486
1487 // Set the time zone to GMT
1488 [dateComponents setTimeZone:[NSTimeZone timeZoneForSecondsFromGMT:0]];
1489
1490 NSInteger year = 0;
1491 while (*p && isASCIIDigit(*p))
1492 year = 10 * year + *p++ - '0';
1493 if (*p++ != '-')
1494 return nil;
1495 [dateComponents setYear:year];
1496
1497 int8_t component;
1498 if (!read2DigitNumber(&p, &component) || *p++ != '-')
1499 return nil;
1500 [dateComponents setMonth:component];
1501
1502 if (!read2DigitNumber(&p, &component) || *p++ != 'T')
1503 return nil;
1504 [dateComponents setDay:component];
1505
1506 if (!read2DigitNumber(&p, &component) || *p++ != ':')
1507 return nil;
1508 [dateComponents setHour:component];
1509
1510 if (!read2DigitNumber(&p, &component) || *p++ != ':')
1511 return nil;
1512 [dateComponents setMinute:component];
1513
1514 if (!read2DigitNumber(&p, &component) || *p++ != 'Z')
1515 return nil;
1516 [dateComponents setSecond:component];
1517
1518 auto calendar = adoptNS([[NSCalendar alloc] initWithCalendarIdentifier:NSCalendarIdentifierGregorian]);
1519 return [calendar dateFromComponents:dateComponents.get()];
1520}

1522static NSInteger _colCompare(id block1, id block2, void *)
1523{
1524 NSInteger col1 = [(NSTextTableBlock *)block1 startingColumn];
1525 NSInteger col2 = [(NSTextTableBlock *)block2 startingColumn];
1526 return ((col1 < col2) ? NSOrderedAscending : ((col1 == col2) ? NSOrderedSame : NSOrderedDescending));
1527}

1529void HTMLConverter::_processMetaElementWithName(NSString *name, NSString *content)
1530{
1531 NSString *key = nil;
1532 if (NSOrderedSame == [@"CocoaVersion" compare:name options:NSCaseInsensitiveSearch]) {
1533 CGFloat versionNumber = [content doubleValue];
1534 if (versionNumber > 0.0) {
1535 // ??? this should be keyed off of version number in future
1536 [_documentAttrs removeObjectForKey:NSConvertedDocumentAttribute];
1537 [_documentAttrs setObject:@(versionNumber) forKey:NSCocoaVersionDocumentAttribute];
1538 }
1539#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
1540 } else if (NSOrderedSame == [@"Generator" compare:name options:NSCaseInsensitiveSearch]) {
1541 key = NSGeneratorDocumentAttribute;
1542#endif
1543 } else if (NSOrderedSame == [@"Keywords" compare:name options:NSCaseInsensitiveSearch]) {
1544 if (content && [content length] > 0) {
1545 NSArray *array;
1546 // ??? need better handling here and throughout
1547 if ([content rangeOfString:@", "].length == 0 && [content rangeOfString:@","].length > 0)
1548 array = [content componentsSeparatedByString:@","];
1549 else if ([content rangeOfString:@", "].length == 0 && [content rangeOfString:@" "].length > 0)
1550 array = [content componentsSeparatedByString:@" "];
1551 else
1552 array = [content componentsSeparatedByString:@", "];
1553 [_documentAttrs setObject:array forKey:NSKeywordsDocumentAttribute];
1554 }
1555 } else if (NSOrderedSame == [@"Author" compare:name options:NSCaseInsensitiveSearch])
1556 key = NSAuthorDocumentAttribute;
1557 else if (NSOrderedSame == [@"LastAuthor" compare:name options:NSCaseInsensitiveSearch])
1558 key = NSEditorDocumentAttribute;
1559 else if (NSOrderedSame == [@"Company" compare:name options:NSCaseInsensitiveSearch])
1560 key = NSCompanyDocumentAttribute;
1561 else if (NSOrderedSame == [@"Copyright" compare:name options:NSCaseInsensitiveSearch])
1562 key = NSCopyrightDocumentAttribute;
1563 else if (NSOrderedSame == [@"Subject" compare:name options:NSCaseInsensitiveSearch])
1564 key = NSSubjectDocumentAttribute;
1565 else if (NSOrderedSame == [@"Description" compare:name options:NSCaseInsensitiveSearch] || NSOrderedSame == [@"Comment" compare:name options:NSCaseInsensitiveSearch])
1566 key = NSCommentDocumentAttribute;
1567 else if (NSOrderedSame == [@"CreationTime" compare:name options:NSCaseInsensitiveSearch]) {
1568 if (content && [content length] > 0) {
1569 NSDate *date = _dateForString(content);
1570 if (date)
1571 [_documentAttrs setObject:date forKey:NSCreationTimeDocumentAttribute];
1572 }
1573 } else if (NSOrderedSame == [@"ModificationTime" compare:name options:NSCaseInsensitiveSearch]) {
1574 if (content && [content length] > 0) {
1575 NSDate *date = _dateForString(content);
1576 if (date)
1577 [_documentAttrs setObject:date forKey:NSModificationTimeDocumentAttribute];
1578 }
1579 }
1580#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
1581 else if (NSOrderedSame == [@"DisplayName" compare:name options:NSCaseInsensitiveSearch] || NSOrderedSame == [@"IndexTitle" compare:name options:NSCaseInsensitiveSearch])
1582 key = NSDisplayNameDocumentAttribute;
1583 else if (NSOrderedSame == [@"robots" compare:name options:NSCaseInsensitiveSearch]) {
1584 if ([content rangeOfString:@"noindex" options:NSCaseInsensitiveSearch].length > 0)
1585 [_documentAttrs setObject:[NSNumber numberWithInteger:1] forKey:NSNoIndexDocumentAttribute];
1586 }
1587#endif
1588 if (key && content && [content length] > 0)
1589 [_documentAttrs setObject:content forKey:key];
1590}

1593{

1604BOOL HTMLConverter::_enterElement(Element& element, BOOL embedded)
1605{
1606 String displayValue = _caches->propertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyDisplay);
1607
1608 if (element.hasTagName(headTag) && !embedded)
1609 _processHeadElement(element);
1610 else if (!displayValue.length() || !(displayValue == "none" || displayValue == "table-column" || displayValue == "table-column-group")) {
1611 if (_caches->isBlockElement(element) && !element.hasTagName(brTag) && !(displayValue == "table-cell" && [_textTables count] == 0)
1612 && !([_textLists count] > 0 && displayValue == "block" && !element.hasTagName(liTag) && !element.hasTagName(ulTag) && !element.hasTagName(olTag)))
1613 _newParagraphForElement(element, element.tagName(), NO, YES);
1614 return YES;
1615 }
1616 return NO;
1617}

1638void HTMLConverter::_addTableForElement(Element *tableElement)
1639{
1640 RetainPtr<NSTextTable> table = adoptNS([(NSTextTable *)[PlatformNSTextTable alloc] init]);
1641 CGFloat cellSpacingVal = 1;
1642 CGFloat cellPaddingVal = 1;
1643 [table setNumberOfColumns:1];
1644 [table setLayoutAlgorithm:NSTextTableAutomaticLayoutAlgorithm];
1645 [table setCollapsesBorders:NO];
1646 [table setHidesEmptyCells:NO];
1647
1648 if (tableElement) {
1649 ASSERT(tableElement);
1650 Element& coreTableElement = *tableElement;
1651
1652 NSString *cellSpacing = coreTableElement.getAttribute(cellspacingAttr);
1653 if (cellSpacing && [cellSpacing length] > 0 && ![cellSpacing hasSuffix:@"%"])
1654 cellSpacingVal = [cellSpacing floatValue];
1655 NSString *cellPadding = coreTableElement.getAttribute(cellpaddingAttr);
1656 if (cellPadding && [cellPadding length] > 0 && ![cellPadding hasSuffix:@"%"])
1657 cellPaddingVal = [cellPadding floatValue];
1658
1659 _fillInBlock(table.get(), coreTableElement, nil, 0, 0, YES);
1660
1661 if (_caches->propertyValueForNode(coreTableElement, CSSPropertyBorderCollapse) == "collapse") {
1662 [table setCollapsesBorders:YES];
1663 cellSpacingVal = 0;
1664 }
1665 if (_caches->propertyValueForNode(coreTableElement, CSSPropertyEmptyCells) == "hide")
1666 [table setHidesEmptyCells:YES];
1667 if (_caches->propertyValueForNode(coreTableElement, CSSPropertyTableLayout) == "fixed")
1668 [table setLayoutAlgorithm:NSTextTableFixedLayoutAlgorithm];
1669 }
1670
1671 [_textTables addObject:table.get()];
1672 [_textTableSpacings addObject:@(cellSpacingVal)];
1673 [_textTablePaddings addObject:@(cellPaddingVal)];
1674 [_textTableRows addObject:[NSNumber numberWithInteger:0]];
1675 [_textTableRowArrays addObject:[NSMutableArray array]];
1676}
1677
1678void HTMLConverter::_addTableCellForElement(Element* element)
1679{
1680 NSTextTable *table = [_textTables lastObject];
1681 NSInteger rowNumber = [[_textTableRows lastObject] integerValue];
1682 NSInteger columnNumber = 0;
1683 NSInteger rowSpan = 1;
1684 NSInteger colSpan = 1;
1685 NSMutableArray *rowArray = [_textTableRowArrays lastObject];
1686 NSUInteger count = [rowArray count];
1687 PlatformColor *color = ([_textTableRowBackgroundColors count] > 0) ? [_textTableRowBackgroundColors lastObject] : nil;
1688 NSTextTableBlock *previousBlock;
1689 CGFloat cellSpacingVal = [[_textTableSpacings lastObject] floatValue];
1690 if ([color isEqual:[PlatformColorClass clearColor]]) color = nil;
1691 for (NSUInteger i = 0; i < count; i++) {
1692 previousBlock = [rowArray objectAtIndex:i];
1693 if (columnNumber >= [previousBlock startingColumn] && columnNumber < [previousBlock startingColumn] + [previousBlock columnSpan])
1694 columnNumber = [previousBlock startingColumn] + [previousBlock columnSpan];
1695 }
1696
1697 RetainPtr<NSTextTableBlock> block;
1698
1699 if (element) {
1700 if (is<HTMLTableCellElement>(*element)) {
1701 HTMLTableCellElement& tableCellElement = downcast<HTMLTableCellElement>(*element);
1702
1703 rowSpan = tableCellElement.rowSpan();
1704 if (rowSpan < 1)
1705 rowSpan = 1;
1706 colSpan = tableCellElement.colSpan();
1707 if (colSpan < 1)
1708 colSpan = 1;
1709 }
1710
1711 block = adoptNS([[PlatformNSTextTableBlock alloc] initWithTable:table startingRow:rowNumber rowSpan:rowSpan startingColumn:columnNumber columnSpan:colSpan]);
1712
1713 String verticalAlign = _caches->propertyValueForNode(*element, CSSPropertyVerticalAlign);
1714
1715 _fillInBlock(block.get(), *element, color, cellSpacingVal / 2, 0, NO);
1716 if (verticalAlign == "middle")
1717 [block setVerticalAlignment:NSTextBlockMiddleAlignment];
1718 else if (verticalAlign == "bottom")
1719 [block setVerticalAlignment:NSTextBlockBottomAlignment];
1720 else if (verticalAlign == "baseline")
1721 [block setVerticalAlignment:NSTextBlockBaselineAlignment];
1722 else if (verticalAlign == "top")
1723 [block setVerticalAlignment:NSTextBlockTopAlignment];
1724 } else {
1725 block = adoptNS([[PlatformNSTextTableBlock alloc] initWithTable:table startingRow:rowNumber rowSpan:rowSpan startingColumn:columnNumber columnSpan:colSpan]);
1726 }
1727
1728 [_textBlocks addObject:block.get()];
1729 [rowArray addObject:block.get()];
1730 [rowArray sortUsingFunction:_colCompare context:NULL];
1731}

1733BOOL HTMLConverter::_processElement(Element& element, NSInteger depth)
1734{
1735 BOOL retval = YES;
1736 BOOL isBlockLevel = _caches->isBlockElement(element);
1737 String displayValue = _caches->propertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyDisplay);
1738 if (isBlockLevel)
1739 [_writingDirectionArray removeAllObjects];
1740 else {
1741 String bidi = _caches->propertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyUnicodeBidi);
1742 if (bidi == "embed") {
1743 NSUInteger val = NSWritingDirectionEmbedding;
1744 if (_caches->propertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyDirection) == "rtl")
1745 val |= NSWritingDirectionRightToLeft;
1746 [_writingDirectionArray addObject:[NSNumber numberWithUnsignedInteger:val]];
1747 } else if (bidi == "bidi-override") {
1748 NSUInteger val = NSWritingDirectionOverride;
1749 if (_caches->propertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyDirection) == "rtl")
1750 val |= NSWritingDirectionRightToLeft;
1751 [_writingDirectionArray addObject:[NSNumber numberWithUnsignedInteger:val]];
1752 }
1753 }
1754 if (displayValue == "table" || ([_textTables count] == 0 && displayValue == "table-row-group")) {
1755 Element* tableElement = &element;
1756 if (displayValue == "table-row-group") {
1757 // If we are starting in medias res, the first thing we see may be the tbody, so go up to the table
1758 tableElement = _blockLevelElementForNode(element.parentInComposedTree());
1759 if (!tableElement || _caches->propertyValueForNode(*tableElement, CSSPropertyDisplay) != "table")
1760 tableElement = &element;
1761 }
1762 while ([_textTables count] > [_textBlocks count])
1763 _addTableCellForElement(nil);
1764 _addTableForElement(tableElement);
1765 } else if (displayValue == "table-footer-group" && [_textTables count] > 0) {
1766 m_textTableFooters.add((__bridge CFTypeRef)[_textTables lastObject], &element);
1767 retval = NO;
1768 } else if (displayValue == "table-row" && [_textTables count] > 0) {
1769 PlatformColor *color = _colorForElement(element, CSSPropertyBackgroundColor);
1770 if (!color)
1771 color = (PlatformColor *)[PlatformColorClass clearColor];
1772 [_textTableRowBackgroundColors addObject:color];
1773 } else if (displayValue == "table-cell") {
1774 while ([_textTables count] < [_textBlocks count] + 1)
1775 _addTableForElement(nil);
1776 _addTableCellForElement(&element);
1777#if ENABLE(ATTACHMENT_ELEMENT)
1778 } else if (is<HTMLAttachmentElement>(element)) {
1779 HTMLAttachmentElement& attachment = downcast<HTMLAttachmentElement>(element);
1780 if (attachment.file()) {
1781 NSURL *url = [NSURL fileURLWithPath:attachment.file()->path()];
1782 if (url)
1783 _addAttachmentForElement(element, url, isBlockLevel, NO);
1784 }
1785 retval = NO;
1786#endif
1787 } else if (element.hasTagName(imgTag)) {
1788 NSString *urlString = element.imageSourceURL();
1789 if (urlString && [urlString length] > 0) {
1790 NSURL *url = element.document().completeURL(stripLeadingAndTrailingHTMLSpaces(urlString));
1791 if (!url)
1792 url = [NSURL _web_URLWithString:[urlString stringByTrimmingCharactersInSet:[NSCharacterSet whitespaceAndNewlineCharacterSet]] relativeToURL:_baseURL.get()];
1793#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
1794 BOOL usePlaceholderImage = NO;
1795#else
1796 BOOL usePlaceholderImage = YES;
1797#endif
1798 if (url)
1799 _addAttachmentForElement(element, url, isBlockLevel, usePlaceholderImage);
1800 }
1801 retval = NO;
1802 } else if (element.hasTagName(objectTag)) {
1803 NSString *baseString = element.getAttribute(codebaseAttr);
1804 NSString *urlString = element.getAttribute(dataAttr);
1805 NSString *declareString = element.getAttribute(declareAttr);
1806 if (urlString && [urlString length] > 0 && ![@"true" isEqualToString:declareString]) {
1807 NSURL *baseURL = nil;
1808 NSURL *url = nil;
1809 if (baseString && [baseString length] > 0) {
1810 baseURL = element.document().completeURL(stripLeadingAndTrailingHTMLSpaces(baseString));
1811 if (!baseURL)
1812 baseURL = [NSURL _web_URLWithString:[baseString stringByTrimmingCharactersInSet:[NSCharacterSet whitespaceAndNewlineCharacterSet]] relativeToURL:_baseURL.get()];
1813 }
1814 if (baseURL)
1815 url = [NSURL _web_URLWithString:[urlString stringByTrimmingCharactersInSet:[NSCharacterSet whitespaceAndNewlineCharacterSet]] relativeToURL:baseURL];
1816 if (!url)
1817 url = element.document().completeURL(stripLeadingAndTrailingHTMLSpaces(urlString));
1818 if (!url)
1819 url = [NSURL _web_URLWithString:[urlString stringByTrimmingCharactersInSet:[NSCharacterSet whitespaceAndNewlineCharacterSet]] relativeToURL:_baseURL.get()];
1820 if (url)
1821 retval = !_addAttachmentForElement(element, url, isBlockLevel, NO);
1822 }
1823 } else if (is<HTMLFrameElementBase>(element)) {
1824 if (Document* contentDocument = downcast<HTMLFrameElementBase>(element).contentDocument()) {
1825 _traverseNode(*contentDocument, depth + 1, true /* embedded */);
1826 retval = NO;
1827 }
1828 } else if (element.hasTagName(brTag)) {
1829 Element* blockElement = _blockLevelElementForNode(element.parentInComposedTree());
1830 NSString *breakClass = element.getAttribute(classAttr);
1831 NSString *blockTag = blockElement ? (NSString *)blockElement->tagName() : nil;
1832 BOOL isExtraBreak = [@"Apple-interchange-newline" isEqualToString:breakClass];
1833 BOOL blockElementIsParagraph = ([@"P" isEqualToString:blockTag] || [@"LI" isEqualToString:blockTag] || ([blockTag hasPrefix:@"H"] && 2 == [blockTag length]));
1834 if (isExtraBreak)
1835 _flags.hasTrailingNewline = YES;
1836 else {
1837 if (blockElement && blockElementIsParagraph)
1838 _newLineForElement(element);
1839 else
1840 _newParagraphForElement(element, element.tagName(), YES, NO);
1841 }
1842 } else if (element.hasTagName(ulTag)) {
1843 RetainPtr<NSTextList> list;
1844 String listStyleType = _caches->propertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyListStyleType);
1845 if (!listStyleType.length())
1846 listStyleType = @"disc";
1847 list = adoptNS([[PlatformNSTextList alloc] initWithMarkerFormat:String("{" + listStyleType + "}") options:0]);
1848 [_textLists addObject:list.get()];
1849 } else if (element.hasTagName(olTag)) {
1850 RetainPtr<NSTextList> list;
1851 String listStyleType = _caches->propertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyListStyleType);
1852 if (!listStyleType.length())
1853 listStyleType = "decimal";
1854 list = adoptNS([[PlatformNSTextList alloc] initWithMarkerFormat:String("{" + listStyleType + "}") options:0]);
1855 if (is<HTMLOListElement>(element)) {
1856 NSInteger startingItemNumber = downcast<HTMLOListElement>(element).start();
1857 [list setStartingItemNumber:startingItemNumber];
1858 }
1859 [_textLists addObject:list.get()];
1860 } else if (element.hasTagName(qTag)) {
1861 _addQuoteForElement(element, YES, _quoteLevel++);
1862 } else if (element.hasTagName(inputTag)) {
1863 if (is<HTMLInputElement>(element)) {
1864 HTMLInputElement& inputElement = downcast<HTMLInputElement>(element);
1865 if (inputElement.type() == "text") {
1866 NSString *value = inputElement.value();
1867 if (value && [value length] > 0)
1868 _addValue(value, element);
1869 }
1870 }
1871 } else if (element.hasTagName(textareaTag)) {
1872 if (is<HTMLTextAreaElement>(element)) {
1873 HTMLTextAreaElement& textAreaElement = downcast<HTMLTextAreaElement>(element);
1874 NSString *value = textAreaElement.value();
1875 if (value && [value length] > 0)
1876 _addValue(value, element);
1877 }
1878 retval = NO;
1879 }
1880 return retval;
1881}

1883void HTMLConverter::_addMarkersToList(NSTextList *list, NSRange range)
1884{
1885 NSInteger itemNum = [list startingItemNumber];
1886 NSString *string = [_attrStr string];
1887 NSString *stringToInsert;
1888 NSDictionary *attrsToInsert = nil;
1889 PlatformFont *font;
1890 NSParagraphStyle *paragraphStyle;
1891 NSTextTab *tab = nil;
1892 NSTextTab *tabToRemove;
1893 NSRange paragraphRange;
1894 NSRange styleRange;
1895 NSUInteger textLength = [_attrStr length];
1896 NSUInteger listIndex;
1897 NSUInteger insertLength;
1898 NSUInteger i;
1899 NSUInteger count;
1900 NSArray *textLists;
1901 CGFloat markerLocation;
1902 CGFloat listLocation;
1903
1904 if (range.length == 0 || range.location >= textLength)
1905 return;
1906 if (NSMaxRange(range) > textLength)
1907 range.length = textLength - range.location;
1908 paragraphStyle = [_attrStr attribute:NSParagraphStyleAttributeName atIndex:range.location effectiveRange:NULL];
1909 if (paragraphStyle) {
1910 textLists = [paragraphStyle textLists];
1911 listIndex = [textLists indexOfObject:list];
1912 if (textLists && listIndex != NSNotFound) {
1913 for (NSUInteger idx = range.location; idx < NSMaxRange(range);) {
1914 paragraphRange = [string paragraphRangeForRange:NSMakeRange(idx, 0)];
1915 paragraphStyle = [_attrStr attribute:NSParagraphStyleAttributeName atIndex:idx effectiveRange:&styleRange];
1916 font = [_attrStr attribute:NSFontAttributeName atIndex:idx effectiveRange:NULL];
1917 if ([[paragraphStyle textLists] count] == listIndex + 1) {
1918 stringToInsert = [NSString stringWithFormat:@"\t%@\t", [list markerForItemNumber:itemNum++]];
1919 insertLength = [stringToInsert length];
1920 attrsToInsert = [PlatformNSTextList _standardMarkerAttributesForAttributes:[_attrStr attributesAtIndex:paragraphRange.location effectiveRange:NULL]];
1921
1922 [_attrStr replaceCharactersInRange:NSMakeRange(paragraphRange.location, 0) withString:stringToInsert];
1923 [_attrStr setAttributes:attrsToInsert range:NSMakeRange(paragraphRange.location, insertLength)];
1924 range.length += insertLength;
1925 paragraphRange.length += insertLength;
1926 if (paragraphRange.location < _domRangeStartIndex)
1927 _domRangeStartIndex += insertLength;
1928
1929 auto newStyle = adoptNS([paragraphStyle mutableCopy]);
1930 listLocation = (listIndex + 1) * 36;
1931 markerLocation = listLocation - 25;
1932 [newStyle setFirstLineHeadIndent:0];
1933 [newStyle setHeadIndent:listLocation];
1934 while ((count = [[newStyle tabStops] count]) > 0) {
1935 for (i = 0, tabToRemove = nil; !tabToRemove && i < count; i++) {
1936 tab = [[newStyle tabStops] objectAtIndex:i];
1937 if ([tab location] <= listLocation)
1938 tabToRemove = tab;
1939 }
1940 if (tabToRemove)
1941 [newStyle removeTabStop:tab];
1942 else
1943 break;
1944 }
1945 [newStyle addTabStop:adoptNS([[PlatformNSTextTab alloc] initWithType:NSLeftTabStopType location:markerLocation]).get()];
1946 [newStyle addTabStop:adoptNS([[PlatformNSTextTab alloc] initWithTextAlignment:NSTextAlignmentNatural location:listLocation options:@{ }]).get()];
1947 [_attrStr addAttribute:NSParagraphStyleAttributeName value:newStyle.get() range:paragraphRange];
1948
1949 idx = NSMaxRange(paragraphRange);
1950 } else {
1951 // skip any deeper-nested lists
1952 idx = NSMaxRange(styleRange);
1953 }
1954 }
1955 }
1956 }
1957}

1959void HTMLConverter::_exitElement(Element& element, NSInteger depth, NSUInteger startIndex)
1960{
1961 String displayValue = _caches->propertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyDisplay);
1962 NSRange range = NSMakeRange(startIndex, [_attrStr length] - startIndex);
1963 if (range.length > 0 && element.hasTagName(aTag))
1964 _addLinkForElement(element, range);
1965 if (!_flags.reachedEnd && _caches->isBlockElement(element)) {
1966 [_writingDirectionArray removeAllObjects];
1967 if (displayValue == "table-cell" && [_textBlocks count] == 0) {
1968 _newTabForElement(element);
1969 } else if ([_textLists count] > 0 && displayValue == "block" && !element.hasTagName(liTag) && !element.hasTagName(ulTag) && !element.hasTagName(olTag)) {
1970 _newLineForElement(element);
1971 } else {
1972 _newParagraphForElement(element, element.tagName(), (range.length == 0), YES);
1973 }
1974 } else if ([_writingDirectionArray count] > 0) {
1975 String bidi = _caches->propertyValueForNode(element, CSSPropertyUnicodeBidi);
1976 if (bidi == "embed" || bidi == "bidi-override")
1977 [_writingDirectionArray removeLastObject];
1978 }
1979 range = NSMakeRange(startIndex, [_attrStr length] - startIndex);
1980 if (displayValue == "table" && [_textTables count] > 0) {
1981 NSTextTable *key = [_textTables lastObject];
1982 Element* footer = m_textTableFooters.get((__bridge CFTypeRef)key);
1983 while ([_textTables count] < [_textBlocks count] + 1)
1984 [_textBlocks removeLastObject];
1985 if (footer) {
1986 _traverseFooterNode(*footer, depth + 1);
1987 m_textTableFooters.remove((__bridge CFTypeRef)key);
1988 }
1989 [_textTables removeLastObject];
1990 [_textTableSpacings removeLastObject];
1991 [_textTablePaddings removeLastObject];
1992 [_textTableRows removeLastObject];
1993 [_textTableRowArrays removeLastObject];
1994 } else if (displayValue == "table-row" && [_textTables count] > 0) {
1995 NSTextTable *table = [_textTables lastObject];
1996 NSTextTableBlock *block;
1997 NSMutableArray *rowArray = [_textTableRowArrays lastObject], *previousRowArray;
1998 NSUInteger i, count;
1999 NSInteger numberOfColumns = [table numberOfColumns];
2000 NSInteger openColumn;
2001 NSInteger rowNumber = [[_textTableRows lastObject] integerValue];
2002 do {
2003 rowNumber++;
2004 previousRowArray = rowArray;
2005 rowArray = [NSMutableArray array];
2006 count = [previousRowArray count];
2007 for (i = 0; i < count; i++) {
2008 block = [previousRowArray objectAtIndex:i];
2009 if ([block startingColumn] + [block columnSpan] > numberOfColumns) numberOfColumns = [block startingColumn] + [block columnSpan];
2010 if ([block startingRow] + [block rowSpan] > rowNumber) [rowArray addObject:block];
2011 }
2012 count = [rowArray count];
2013 openColumn = 0;
2014 for (i = 0; i < count; i++) {
2015 block = [rowArray objectAtIndex:i];
2016 if (openColumn >= [block startingColumn] && openColumn < [block startingColumn] + [block columnSpan]) openColumn = [block startingColumn] + [block columnSpan];
2017 }
2018 } while (openColumn >= numberOfColumns);
2019 if ((NSUInteger)numberOfColumns > [table numberOfColumns])
2020 [table setNumberOfColumns:numberOfColumns];
2021 [_textTableRows removeLastObject];
2022 [_textTableRows addObject:[NSNumber numberWithInteger:rowNumber]];
2023 [_textTableRowArrays removeLastObject];
2024 [_textTableRowArrays addObject:rowArray];
2025 if ([_textTableRowBackgroundColors count] > 0)
2026 [_textTableRowBackgroundColors removeLastObject];
2027 } else if (displayValue == "table-cell" && [_textBlocks count] > 0) {
2028 while ([_textTables count] > [_textBlocks count]) {
2029 [_textTables removeLastObject];
2030 [_textTableSpacings removeLastObject];
2031 [_textTablePaddings removeLastObject];
2032 [_textTableRows removeLastObject];
2033 [_textTableRowArrays removeLastObject];
2034 }
2035 [_textBlocks removeLastObject];
2036 } else if ((element.hasTagName(ulTag) || element.hasTagName(olTag)) && [_textLists count] > 0) {
2037 NSTextList *list = [_textLists lastObject];
2038 _addMarkersToList(list, range);
2039 [_textLists removeLastObject];
2040 } else if (element.hasTagName(qTag)) {
2041 _addQuoteForElement(element, NO, --_quoteLevel);
2042 } else if (element.hasTagName(spanTag)) {
2043 NSString *className = element.getAttribute(classAttr);
2044 NSMutableString *mutableString;
2045 NSUInteger i, count = 0;
2046 unichar c;
2047 if ([@"Apple-converted-space" isEqualToString:className]) {
2048 mutableString = [_attrStr mutableString];
2049 for (i = range.location; i < NSMaxRange(range); i++) {
2050 c = [mutableString characterAtIndex:i];
2051 if (0xa0 == c)
2052 [mutableString replaceCharactersInRange:NSMakeRange(i, 1) withString:@" "];
2053 }
2054 } else if ([@"Apple-converted-tab" isEqualToString:className]) {
2055 mutableString = [_attrStr mutableString];
2056 for (i = range.location; i < NSMaxRange(range); i++) {
2057 NSRange rangeToReplace = NSMakeRange(NSNotFound, 0);
2058 c = [mutableString characterAtIndex:i];
2059 if (' ' == c || 0xa0 == c) {
2060 count++;
2061 if (count >= 4 || i + 1 >= NSMaxRange(range))
2062 rangeToReplace = NSMakeRange(i + 1 - count, count);
2063 } else {
2064 if (count > 0)
2065 rangeToReplace = NSMakeRange(i - count, count);
2066 }
2067 if (rangeToReplace.length > 0) {
2068 [mutableString replaceCharactersInRange:rangeToReplace withString:@"\t"];
2069 range.length -= (rangeToReplace.length - 1);
2070 i -= (rangeToReplace.length - 1);
2071 if (NSMaxRange(rangeToReplace) <= _domRangeStartIndex) {
2072 _domRangeStartIndex -= (rangeToReplace.length - 1);
2073 } else if (rangeToReplace.location < _domRangeStartIndex) {
2074 _domRangeStartIndex = rangeToReplace.location;
2075 }
2076 count = 0;
2077 }
2078 }
2079 }
2080 }
2081}

2083void HTMLConverter::_processText(CharacterData& characterData)
2084{
2085 NSUInteger textLength = [_attrStr length];
2086 unichar lastChar = (textLength > 0) ? [[_attrStr string] characterAtIndex:textLength - 1] : '\n';
2087 BOOL suppressLeadingSpace = ((_flags.isSoft && lastChar == ' ') || lastChar == '\n' || lastChar == '\r' || lastChar == '\t' || lastChar == NSParagraphSeparatorCharacter || lastChar == NSLineSeparatorCharacter || lastChar == NSFormFeedCharacter || lastChar == WebNextLineCharacter);
2088 NSRange rangeToReplace = NSMakeRange(textLength, 0);
2089
2090 String originalString = characterData.data();
2091 unsigned startOffset = 0;
2092 unsigned endOffset = originalString.length();
2093 if (&characterData == m_start.containerNode()) {
2094 startOffset = m_start.offsetInContainerNode();
2095 _domRangeStartIndex = [_attrStr length];
2096 _flags.reachedStart = YES;
2097 }
2098 if (&characterData == m_end.containerNode()) {
2099 endOffset = m_end.offsetInContainerNode();
2100 _flags.reachedEnd = YES;
2101 }
2102 if ((startOffset > 0 || endOffset < originalString.length()) && endOffset >= startOffset)
2103 originalString = originalString.substring(startOffset, endOffset - startOffset);
2104 String outputString = originalString;
2105
2106 // FIXME: Use RenderText's content instead.
2107 bool wasSpace = false;
2108 if (_caches->propertyValueForNode(characterData, CSSPropertyWhiteSpace).startsWith("pre")) {
2109 if (textLength && originalString.length() && _flags.isSoft) {
2110 unichar c = originalString.characterAt(0);
2111 if (c == '\n' || c == '\r' || c == NSParagraphSeparatorCharacter || c == NSLineSeparatorCharacter || c == NSFormFeedCharacter || c == WebNextLineCharacter)
2112 rangeToReplace = NSMakeRange(textLength - 1, 1);
2113 }
2114 } else {
2115 unsigned count = originalString.length();
2116 bool wasLeading = true;
2117 StringBuilder builder;
2118 LChar noBreakSpaceRepresentation = 0;
2119 for (unsigned i = 0; i < count; i++) {
2120 UChar c = originalString.characterAt(i);
2121 bool isWhitespace = c == ' ' || c == '\n' || c == '\r' || c == '\t' || c == 0xc || c == 0x200b;
2122 if (isWhitespace)
2123 wasSpace = (!wasLeading || !suppressLeadingSpace);
2124 else {
2125 if (wasSpace)
2126 builder.append(' ');
2127 if (c != noBreakSpace)
2128 builder.append(c);
2129 else {
2130 if (!noBreakSpaceRepresentation)
2131 noBreakSpaceRepresentation = _caches->propertyValueForNode(characterData, CSSPropertyWebkitNbspMode) == "space" ? ' ' : noBreakSpace;
2132 builder.append(noBreakSpaceRepresentation);
2133 }
2134 wasSpace = false;
2135 wasLeading = false;
2136 }
2137 }
2138 if (wasSpace)
2139 builder.append(' ');
2140 outputString = builder.toString();
2141 }
2142
2143 if (outputString.length()) {
2144 String textTransform = _caches->propertyValueForNode(characterData, CSSPropertyTextTransform);
2145 if (textTransform == "capitalize")
2146 outputString = capitalize(outputString, ' '); // FIXME: Needs to take locale into account to work correctly.
2147 else if (textTransform == "uppercase")
2148 outputString = outputString.convertToUppercaseWithoutLocale(); // FIXME: Needs locale to work correctly.
2149 else if (textTransform == "lowercase")
2150 outputString = outputString.convertToLowercaseWithoutLocale(); // FIXME: Needs locale to work correctly.
2151
2152 [_attrStr replaceCharactersInRange:rangeToReplace withString:outputString];
2153 rangeToReplace.length = outputString.length();
2154 if (rangeToReplace.length)
2155 [_attrStr setAttributes:aggregatedAttributesForAncestors(characterData) range:rangeToReplace];
2156 _flags.isSoft = wasSpace;
2157 }
2158}

2160void HTMLConverter::_traverseNode(Node& node, unsigned depth, bool embedded)
2161{
2162 if (_flags.reachedEnd)
2163 return;
2164 if (!_flags.reachedStart && !_caches->isAncestorsOfStartToBeConverted(node))
2165 return;
2166
2167 unsigned startOffset = 0;
2168 unsigned endOffset = UINT_MAX;
2169 bool isStart = false;
2170 bool isEnd = false;
2171 if (&node == m_start.containerNode()) {
2172 startOffset = m_start.computeOffsetInContainerNode();
2173 isStart = true;
2174 _flags.reachedStart = YES;
2175 }
2176 if (&node == m_end.containerNode()) {
2177 endOffset = m_end.computeOffsetInContainerNode();
2178 isEnd = true;
2179 }
2180
2181 if (node.isDocumentNode() || node.isDocumentFragment()) {
2182 Node* child = node.firstChild();
2183 ASSERT(child == firstChildInComposedTreeIgnoringUserAgentShadow(node));
2184 for (NSUInteger i = 0; child; i++) {
2185 if (isStart && i == startOffset)
2186 _domRangeStartIndex = [_attrStr length];
2187 if ((!isStart || startOffset <= i) && (!isEnd || endOffset > i))
2188 _traverseNode(*child, depth + 1, embedded);
2189 if (isEnd && i + 1 >= endOffset)
2190 _flags.reachedEnd = YES;
2191 if (_flags.reachedEnd)
2192 break;
2193 ASSERT(child->nextSibling() == nextSiblingInComposedTreeIgnoringUserAgentShadow(*child));
2194 child = child->nextSibling();
2195 }
2196 } else if (is<Element>(node)) {
2197 Element& element = downcast<Element>(node);
2198 if (_enterElement(element, embedded)) {
2199 NSUInteger startIndex = [_attrStr length];
2200 if (_processElement(element, depth)) {
2201 if (auto* shadowRoot = shadowRootIgnoringUserAgentShadow(element)) // Traverse through shadow root to detect start and end.
2202 _traverseNode(*shadowRoot, depth + 1, embedded);
2203 else {
2204 auto* child = firstChildInComposedTreeIgnoringUserAgentShadow(node);
2205 for (NSUInteger i = 0; child; i++) {
2206 if (isStart && i == startOffset)
2207 _domRangeStartIndex = [_attrStr length];
2208 if ((!isStart || startOffset <= i) && (!isEnd || endOffset > i))
2209 _traverseNode(*child, depth + 1, embedded);
2210 if (isEnd && i + 1 >= endOffset)
2211 _flags.reachedEnd = YES;
2212 if (_flags.reachedEnd)
2213 break;
2214 child = nextSiblingInComposedTreeIgnoringUserAgentShadow(*child);
2215 }
2216 }
2217 _exitElement(element, depth, std::min(startIndex, [_attrStr length]));
2218 }
2219 }
2220 } else if (node.nodeType() == Node::TEXT_NODE)
2221 _processText(downcast<CharacterData>(node));
2222
2223 if (isEnd)
2224 _flags.reachedEnd = YES;
2225}
