2227void HTMLConverter::_traverseFooterNode(Element& element, unsigned depth)
2228{
2229 if (_flags.reachedEnd)
2230 return;
2231 if (!_flags.reachedStart && !_caches->isAncestorsOfStartToBeConverted(element))
2232 return;
2233
2234 unsigned startOffset = 0;
2235 unsigned endOffset = UINT_MAX;
2236 bool isStart = false;
2237 bool isEnd = false;
2238 if (&element == m_start.containerNode()) {
2239 startOffset = m_start.computeOffsetInContainerNode();
2240 isStart = true;
2241 _flags.reachedStart = YES;
2242 }
2243 if (&element == m_end.containerNode()) {
2244 endOffset = m_end.computeOffsetInContainerNode();
2245 isEnd = true;
2246 }
2247
2248 if (_enterElement(element, YES)) {
2249 NSUInteger startIndex = [_attrStr length];
2250 if (_processElement(element, depth)) {
2251 auto* child = firstChildInComposedTreeIgnoringUserAgentShadow(element);
2252 for (NSUInteger i = 0; child; i++) {
2253 if (isStart && i == startOffset)
2254 _domRangeStartIndex = [_attrStr length];
2255 if ((!isStart || startOffset <= i) && (!isEnd || endOffset > i))
2256 _traverseNode(*child, depth + 1, true /* embedded */);
2257 if (isEnd && i + 1 >= endOffset)
2258 _flags.reachedEnd = YES;
2259 if (_flags.reachedEnd)
2260 break;
2261 child = nextSiblingInComposedTreeIgnoringUserAgentShadow(*child);
2262 }
2263 _exitElement(element, depth, startIndex);
2264 }
2265 }
2266 if (isEnd)
2267 _flags.reachedEnd = YES;
2268}

2270void HTMLConverter::_adjustTrailingNewline()
2271{
2272 NSUInteger textLength = [_attrStr length];
2273 unichar lastChar = (textLength > 0) ? [[_attrStr string] characterAtIndex:textLength - 1] : 0;
2274 BOOL alreadyHasTrailingNewline = (lastChar == '\n' || lastChar == '\r' || lastChar == NSParagraphSeparatorCharacter || lastChar == NSLineSeparatorCharacter || lastChar == WebNextLineCharacter);
2275 if (_flags.hasTrailingNewline && !alreadyHasTrailingNewline)
2276 [_attrStr replaceCharactersInRange:NSMakeRange(textLength, 0) withString:@"\n"];
2277}

2279Node* HTMLConverterCaches::cacheAncestorsOfStartToBeConverted(const Position& start, const Position& end)
2280{
2281 auto commonAncestor = commonInclusiveAncestor(start, end);
2282 Node* ancestor = start.containerNode();
2283
2284 while (ancestor) {
2285 m_ancestorsUnderCommonAncestor.add(*ancestor);
2286 if (ancestor == commonAncestor)
2287 break;
2288 ancestor = ancestor->parentInComposedTree();
2289 }
2290
2291 return commonAncestor;
2292}

2354// This function uses TextIterator, which makes offsets in its result compatible with HTML editing.
2355AttributedString editingAttributedString(const SimpleRange& range, IncludeImages includeImages)
2356{
2357 auto fontManager = [NSFontManager sharedFontManager];
2358 auto string = adoptNS([[NSMutableAttributedString alloc] init]);
2359 auto attrs = adoptNS([[NSMutableDictionary alloc] init]);
2360 NSUInteger stringLength = 0;
2361 for (TextIterator it(range); !it.atEnd(); it.advance()) {
2362 auto node = it.node();
2363
2364 if (includeImages == IncludeImages::Yes && is<HTMLImageElement>(node)) {
2365 auto fileWrapper = fileWrapperForElement(downcast<HTMLImageElement>(*node));
2366 auto attachment = adoptNS([[NSTextAttachment alloc] initWithFileWrapper:fileWrapper.get()]);
2367 [string appendAttributedString:[NSAttributedString attributedStringWithAttachment:attachment.get()]];
2368 }
2369
2370 auto currentTextLength = it.text().length();
2371 if (!currentTextLength)
2372 continue;
2373
2374 // In some cases the text iterator emits text that is not associated with a node.
2375 // In those cases, base the style on the container.
2376 if (!node)
2377 node = it.range().start.container.ptr();
2378 auto renderer = node->renderer();
2379 ASSERT(renderer);
2380 if (!renderer)
2381 continue;
2382 auto& style = renderer->style();
2383 if (style.textDecorationsInEffect() & TextDecoration::Underline)
2384 [attrs setObject:[NSNumber numberWithInteger:NSUnderlineStyleSingle] forKey:NSUnderlineStyleAttributeName];
2385 if (style.textDecorationsInEffect() & TextDecoration::LineThrough)
2386 [attrs setObject:[NSNumber numberWithInteger:NSUnderlineStyleSingle] forKey:NSStrikethroughStyleAttributeName];
2387 if (auto font = style.fontCascade().primaryFont().getCTFont())
2388 [attrs setObject:toNSFont(font) forKey:NSFontAttributeName];
2389 else
2390 [attrs setObject:[fontManager convertFont:WebDefaultFont() toSize:style.fontCascade().primaryFont().platformData().size()] forKey:NSFontAttributeName];
2391
2392 auto textAlignment = NSTextAlignmentNatural;
2393 switch (style.textAlign()) {
2394 case TextAlignMode::Right:
2395 case TextAlignMode::WebKitRight:
2396 textAlignment = NSTextAlignmentRight;
2397 break;
2398 case TextAlignMode::Left:
2399 case TextAlignMode::WebKitLeft:
2400 textAlignment = NSTextAlignmentLeft;
2401 break;
2402 case TextAlignMode::Center:
2403 case TextAlignMode::WebKitCenter:
2404 textAlignment = NSTextAlignmentCenter;
2405 break;
2406 case TextAlignMode::Justify:
2407 textAlignment = NSTextAlignmentJustified;
2408 break;
2409 case TextAlignMode::Start:
2410 if (style.hasExplicitlySetDirection())
2411 textAlignment = style.isLeftToRightDirection() ? NSTextAlignmentLeft : NSTextAlignmentRight;
2412 break;
2413 case TextAlignMode::End:
2414 textAlignment = style.isLeftToRightDirection() ? NSTextAlignmentRight : NSTextAlignmentLeft;
2415 break;
2416 default:
2417 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
2418 break;
2419 }
2420
2421 if (textAlignment != NSTextAlignmentNatural) {
2422 auto paragraphStyle = adoptNS(NSParagraphStyle.defaultParagraphStyle.mutableCopy);
2423 [paragraphStyle setAlignment:textAlignment];
2424 [attrs setObject:paragraphStyle.get() forKey:NSParagraphStyleAttributeName];
2425 }
2426
2427 Color foregroundColor = style.visitedDependentColorWithColorFilter(CSSPropertyColor);
2428 if (foregroundColor.isVisible())
2429 [attrs setObject:nsColor(foregroundColor) forKey:NSForegroundColorAttributeName];
2430 else
2431 [attrs removeObjectForKey:NSForegroundColorAttributeName];
2432
2433 Color backgroundColor = style.visitedDependentColorWithColorFilter(CSSPropertyBackgroundColor);
2434 if (backgroundColor.isVisible())
2435 [attrs setObject:nsColor(backgroundColor) forKey:NSBackgroundColorAttributeName];
2436 else
2437 [attrs removeObjectForKey:NSBackgroundColorAttributeName];
2438
2439 RetainPtr<NSString> text;
2440 if (style.nbspMode() == NBSPMode::Normal)
2441 text = it.text().createNSStringWithoutCopying();
2442 else
2443 text = it.text().toString().replace(noBreakSpace, ' ');
2444
2445 [string replaceCharactersInRange:NSMakeRange(stringLength, 0) withString:text.get()];
2446 [string setAttributes:attrs.get() range:NSMakeRange(stringLength, currentTextLength)];
2447 stringLength += currentTextLength;
2448 }
2449
2450 return { WTFMove(string), nil };
2451}
